item.title: CVE-2020-5623|2024-08-04T08:39:25.781Z -- nitori%20holdings%20co.%2C%20ltd. -- nitori%20app%20for%20android%20and%20nitori%20app%20for%20ios
item.description: NITORI App for Android versions 6.0.4 and earlier and NITORI App for iOS versions 6.0.2 and earlier allow remote attackers to lead a user to access an arbitrary website via the vulnerable App. As a result, the user may become a victim of a phishing attack.
